flowchart TD
  R[User asks Hermes to add/update Job] --> P[Parse requirements]
  P --> W[Use prompts/workflows/add-job-to-repo.md]
  W --> Y[Create or update jobs/category/name.yaml]
  Y --> F[Check required fields]
  F --> S[Secret scan]
  S --> D[Show diff/status to user]
  C[Cron Runner] --> L[Load enabled registry Jobs]
  L --> E[Execute via Job Prompt]
  E --> O[Output sanitized result]
  E --> M[Emit memory candidates only]
